www.nme.com/news/film/james-cameron-calls-the-terminator-cringeworthy-in-parts-40-years-on-from-release-3795787">去年在庆祝电影40周年的同时，在“零件”中称这部电影为“ Cringworty”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-terminator-live-tour-coming-to-the-uk-this-year-3846938">今年即将参加英国的“终结者现场直播”巡回</a>演出首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
